{"tid":1826611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭麗琼趕便衣警離場","createTime":"2020-01-16T09:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T20:06:45.000Z","uid":71393,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"18084c138476304841e170acec836a61ceece872","tid":1826611,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T09:26:36.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強出席中西區區議會　主席鄭麗琼趕拒出示委任證便衣警離場　禁撐警人士鼓掌<br />\n<br />\n中西區區議會今日（16日）舉行第二次大會，討論涉及警方的問題，警務處處長鄧炳強亦會出席會議，有多名便衣警在會上戒備。在會議上，中西區區議會主席民主黨鄭麗琼先要求在場便衣警員出示委任證，有一名穿著背心的便衣警因未有出示委任證被趕離場。<br />\n鄭麗琼又一度要求在鄧炳強發言後鼓掌的人士立即離場，後提出作最後警告，最終無人離場，但旁聽的撐警人士也停止了拍掌。<br />\n<br />\n在會議開始前，鄭麗琼要求在場便衣警員出示委任證，又稱若有便衣警員不展示委任證，將會被要求離開會議室，或以旁聽身份在會議室外等候。鄭又表示，由於在場較多長者，希望便衣警員及區議員助理讓座。多名的便衣警在鄭多番的堅持及督促下，展示了委任證，包括警務處助理處長（支援）林曉彤。<br />\n及後，會議進行期間，一名穿著背心的便衣警因未有出示委任證，遭鄭麗琼要求離場，鄭斥：「冇委任證就唔好進入會議室」，又批該名便衣警「咁唔尊重」，該便衣警最終離場。<br />\n鄧炳強隨後到達會場，有人喊「支持警隊﹑嚴正執法」，亦有人高叫反對警暴的口號。鄧炳強在會上發言後，坐在會上最後排的旁聽人士紛紛鼓掌，鄭麗琼隨即喝停，並要求鼓掌人士立即離場，指是次會議「非常莊嚴﹑嚴肅」，「誰人發言也不用拍手掌，也不用噓聲」。鄭多次要求有份拍手的人士離開，但無人離場，鄭最終表示，她已經「三次」警告，若再有任何人拍手，該名人士將被趕離場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E4%B8%AD%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%84%AD%E9%BA%97%E7%90%BC%E8%B6%95%E6%8B%92%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4-%E7%A6%81%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E9%BC%93%E6%8E%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E9%2584%25AD%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2590%25BC%25E8%25B6%2595%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E9%25BC%2593%25E6%258E%258C%2F&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=ebb81e49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E9%2584%25AD%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2590%25BC%25E8%25B6%2595%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E9%25BC%2593%25E6%258E%258C%2F&h=d1641bd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E4%B8%AD%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%84%AD%E9%BA%97%E7%90%BC%E8%B6%95%E6%8B%92%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4-%E7%A6%81%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E9%BC%93%E6%8E%8C/</a><br />\n<br />\n主席好有官威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d3eb14617bbf456735c8e79e859b1d9b8261a6","tid":1826611,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T09:29:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">歐美議員講野又無人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響task2呀 幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=896ca819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style