警最終離場。<br />\n鄧炳強隨後到達會場，有人喊「支持警隊﹑嚴正執法」，亦有人高叫反對警暴的口號。鄧炳強在會上發言後，坐在會上最後排的旁聽人士紛紛鼓掌，鄭麗琼隨即喝停，並要求鼓掌人士立即離場，指是次會議「非常莊嚴﹑嚴肅」，「誰人發言也不用拍手掌，也不用噓聲」。鄭多次要求有份拍手的人士離開，但無人離場，鄭最終表示，她已經「三次」警告，若再有任何人拍手，該名人士將被趕離場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E4%B8%AD%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%84%AD%E9%BA%97%E7%90%BC%E8%B6%95%E6%8B%92%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4-%E7%A6%81%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E9%BC%93%E6%8E%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E9%2584%25AD%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2590%25BC%25E8%25B6%2595%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E9%25BC%2593%25E6%258E%258C%2F&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=ebb81e49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E9%2584%25AD%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2590%25BC%25E8%25B6%2595%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E9%25BC%2593%25E6%258E%258C%2F&h=d1641bd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E4%